songs.title: Good Enough
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]
Every single mother cries so much
And be strong for me and suck it up
Did what we had to just to make it work
I know you love us, do anything for us if you're good
Nothing's the same now that you're gone (And I miss you)
But I continue to stay strong for you (And that's the truth)
Nothing ever was good enough for you (Good for you)
You're the reason why I act so tough, it's true
We got issues, we don't clean it up
Before it takes over, before I get over you

[Outro]
Nothing ever wants to, wants to, wants to
Over you
